Nina Py Brozovich bụ onye na-ahụ maka ihu igwe na Bolivia
Ọ bụ ya guzobere Friday For Future na Bolivia. Ọ bụ akụkụ nke United Nations Youth Climate Summit.
Ọrụ ya apụtala na Bolivian Express, Pagina Siete, na Fridays for Future kwa izu. Ọ bụ akụkụ nke mkpọsa UNICEF "Otu Ọgbọ". Ọ bụ onye ọrụ afọ ofufo na La Senda Verde.
